{
  "id": "adv_event_2205_01_04",
  "title": "心紡ぎ合う輝きの競演 4話 本当にやりたいこと",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "私、が……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What about me…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "うん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "今のお姉ちゃん、全然キラキラしてない",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Onee-chan right now‚ you're not shining at all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "千紗。……どういうこと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa… What do you mean?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "ちゃんと説明してちょうだい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Please explain properly.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "お姉ちゃんは、ずっと",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Onee-chan has always been",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "私のことを立てようとしてくれてる",
      "translations": {
        "en": "trying to support me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.0468545913,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "それがユニットのためだって言うけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She says it's for the sake of the team…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "それなら、お姉ちゃんはどうしてそんなに辛そうなの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But then‚ why does Onee-chan look so troubled?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "私だって……いつまでもお姉ちゃんに支えられなくても",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even if I can't always rely on Onee-chan forever‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 27.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "一人でも大丈夫だから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll be fine on my own.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "私にも……お姉ちゃんを支えさせて？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let me support Onee-chan too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 35.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "千紗……で、でも、私は……お姉ちゃんだから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa… B-but‚ I'm… your Onee-chan‚ so…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "あなたを、支えないと……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have to support you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "（あ……お姉ちゃん、辛そう……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Ah… Onee-chan looks troubled…)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "（でも、ここでやめたら、私達、前に進めない……！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(But if we stop here‚ we won't be able to move forward…!)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "こ、このままお姉ちゃんが譲っちゃうなら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I'll step forward for real",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "私が、ほんとに前に出ちゃうんだから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "if Onee-chan is going to give up…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "ち、千紗……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ch-Chisa…?",
