      },
      "startTime": 69.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "私ばっかり目立っちゃうよ！　それでも……いいの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'll end up overshadowing you! Is that… okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "それ、は……でも、私は……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… but I…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "お姉ちゃん……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Onee-chan…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 82.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんが本当にやりたいことはなんなの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What is it that you really want to do?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "私の……本当にやりたいこと……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What I… truly want to do…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "今のお姉ちゃんは自分を殺してると思う",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I think our current Onee-chan is killing herself.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.1333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "これじゃあバトルだって勝てないし、何より……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We won't win battles like this‚ and above all…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.7666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "私は……そんなお姉ちゃん、見たくないよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I don't want to see Onee-chan like this…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "月ストのお姉ちゃんも好きだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I love the Onee-chan from Moon Tempest‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "私はこのユニットで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In this team…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.4333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "小学生の時、私の前でアイドルの真似をして見せて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to see the sparkling Onee-chan",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04-chs013.m4a",
      "text": "くれてた時の、キラキラしたお姉ちゃんがまた見たい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "who imitated idols in front of me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "好きなことを自由にやって、楽しそうなお姉ちゃんに",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And the Onee-chan who enjoys doing what she loves‚",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04-chs014.m4a",
      "text": "また……会いたいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want to see her again…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "千紗……ごめんね、ありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Chisa… I'm sorry‚ thank you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2205_01_04-chs015.m4a",
      "text": "ううん……私こそ、ごめんね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No… I should be the one saying sorry.",
